title: Crimp Supply Ultra-Flexible Car Battery/Welding Cable - 6 Gauge, (20 Feet Red/20 Feet Black) - and 5 Copper Lugs
features: Includes 5 seamless copper lugs with 3/8" stud.

description: Made in the USA! Also known as welding cable this very flexible battery cable can easily lace throughout an engine compartment and around tight turns with ease. Highly flexible annealed 30 gauge bare copper conductors 260 strands insulated with an EPDM jacket and paper separator. Resists abrasion cut tear flame grease oil and water.
